r />\n最緊要自己用得自然"},{"pid":"28fcf58189a354f1a78d86e4a8fd14976c85c742","tid":508530,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a95acf4f7cd0bce583443107bed257c9aaac9f3","tid":508530,"uid":19978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T10:55:35.000Z","msg":"兩個人相對已然冰冷的瞳孔，有鋒利的剪刀分手"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T10:58:06.000Z","msg":"嗯.....我諗起剪J<br />\n<br />\n但我估你講立會剪布（呢度時事台）<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d74ddebafe48015bec3fb691eacd841cd5d423c","tid":508530,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T11:04:10.000Z","msg":"當初一國兩制，係中央收復台灣的試板，然而主權移交二十年，台灣在國民黨親共下，逐漸失去獨立的行政治權，與此同時，一國兩制於香港亦愈見名存實亡。<br />\n<br />\n在自治的黃昏，垂懸的芒草，是在掙扎，還是哀求憐憫？在寒風與日落希微的餘暉之中，究竟人將何去何從？"},{"pid":"664bffa92ba37829c65cfb6cc5b71d72f2556a66","tid":508530,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T14:40:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你上個po無復我<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>Where</blockquote><br />\n<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>William Lilly 再世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁佢啲書必讀既</blockquote><br />\n我見人講佢d concept有d問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(native方面)<br />\n<br />\n其實巴打係點入手學<br />\n<br />\n我見市面上無乜太多classical predictive嘅astrology書<br />\n<br />\n我自己好想學mudane astrology嘅野</blockquote></blockquote>乜都睇下自然搵到岩自己既風格<br />\n<br />\n唔同作者/占星家理論一定有唔同<br />\n<br />\n除非拜師，否則邊派勁啲既言論唔使理<br />\n<br />\n最緊要自己用得自然</blockquote><br />\n咁你初學係睇咩書架呢<br />\n因為好多出名嘅都係例如william lilly,都係n年前寫落，比較難明"},{"pid":"a4bc79a51c3512d7d2199d304ff6c495d5ebde29","tid":508530,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"664bffa92ba37829c65cfb6cc5b71d72f2556a66","tid":508530,"uid":35870,"like":0